text: Patrik Džalto (born 19 February 1997) is a Croatian footballer who plays as a forward, most recently for Austria Klagenfurt in the Austrian Football Second League. ==Career== In summer 2016, Džalto joined SSV Jahn Regensburg on loan from Bayer 04 Leverkusen for the 2016–17 season. In June 2017, he signed permanently, agreeing to a one-year contract.
